    "The complete grammar analysis extends to Danish, Dutch, Finnish, French, German, Portuguese, and Spanish, whereas other tools work with a wider range of languages and language varieties.",
    "Additional language varieties will be supported over time.",
    "The ability of Open Brain AI to scale concerning new languages and language variety support highlights a critical difference between computational models and traditional manual assessment techniques, which require expert knowledge for translation, standardization, and evaluation to maintain crosslinguistic psychometric properties, such as the reliability and validity of tests.",
    "The Open Brain AI platform offers access to these trained models for clinicians and teachers and makes them available.",
    "Second, Open Brain AI does not collect data provided for analysis."
